text: Artaulovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Aksaitovsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 221 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 5 km from Aksaitovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Artaulovo
